      "acceptanceCriteria": "Physics assumptions justified for the COU loading regime; nonlinear material behavior captured.",
      "rationale": "Bilinear isotropic hardening plasticity (BISO) adopted for Ti-6Al-4V. Large-deformation formulation (NLGEOM ON) active. Frictional contact (mu=0.2) at screw-rod and screw-vertebral body block interfaces. Model form appropriate for quasi-static compression-bending up to 40 mm displacement."
    },
