      "rationale": "Elastic modulus, yield strength, and tangent modulus sourced from the Ti-6Al-4V material property dataset (dataVintage 2025-09-05). Geometric dimensions from production drawing revision D. Uncertainty in material inputs propagated via Monte Carlo (n=500); contribution to QoI uncertainty <3%. Re-validation of material inputs against the February 2026 model revision is planned for Q2 2026 but has not yet been completed."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
