      "rationale": "Three primary QoI compared: stiffness (4.2%, E/uval=1.31), yield force (6.8%, E/uval=1.57), force at 40 mm (7.3%, E/uval=1.74). All within acceptance bounds. Experimental uncertainty estimated via GUM methodology from calibration records of both laboratories."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
